  <brief_title>Investigation of Lumbo-sacral Instability Using Custom Made Table - a Pilot Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Radiologic Presentation of Lumbo-sacral Instability Using a Custom Made Table - a Pilot Study</official_title>
